    {
        "content": "<p>That is exactly what I did, I modified the default <code>Methods</code> inside <code>Lean.Meta.Simp.simp</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code>  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">none</span>   <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">Simp.main</span> <span class=\"n\">e</span> <span class=\"n\">ctx</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">methods</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">Simp.DefaultMethods.methods</span>\n                                          <span class=\"bp\">|&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">pres.foldl</span>  <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">λ</span> <span class=\"n\">m</span> <span class=\"n\">p</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">m.appendPre</span> <span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n                                          <span class=\"bp\">|&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">posts.foldl</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">λ</span> <span class=\"n\">m</span> <span class=\"n\">p</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">m.appendPost</span> <span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Yeah I understand that this is not a priority right now, I will find some work around it.</p>",
